eira  ||Points\n|-\n|{{no2}}Loss||{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Vinny Magalh\u00e3es]] || Referee Decision || rowspan=3|ADCC 2015||Absolute|| September 30, 2015 ||rowspan=3|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[S\u00e3o Paulo]]\n|-\n|{{no2}}Loss||{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Lucas Lepri]] || Points (0-10)||rowspan=2|-77kg||rowspan=2|September 29, 2015\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|USA}} Dillon Danis || Submission (heel hook)\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|BRA}} Jo\u00e3o Miyao  || Judges Decision || FIVE Super League||Superfight|| August 8, 2015 ||{{flagicon|USA}} [[New York City]], [[New York (state)|NY]]\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|USA}} Rob Greenidge  || Submission (calf slicer) || rowspan=3|Grapplers Quest: All Star Pro||rowspan=3|-77kg|| rowspan=3|June 6, 2015 ||rowspan=3|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Edison, New Jersey|Edison]], [[New Jersey|NJ]]\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|USA}} Joe Solecki  || Submission (heel hook)\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|USA}} Jordan Tabor  || Submission (guillotine choke)\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|USA}} Josh Hinger  || Fastest Escape || rowspan=4|EBI 3||rowspan=4|-170lbs|| rowspan=4|March 22, 2015 ||rowspan=4|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Los Angeles]], [[California|CA]]\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|USA}} Eddie Cummings  || Submission (triangle armbar)\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|ARM}} [[Karen Darabedyan]]  || Fastest Escape\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|USA}} Josh Valles  || Submission (heel hook)\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|CUB}} [[Javier Vazquez (fighter)|Javier Vazquez]]  || Submission (triangle choke) || Gracie Nationals||Superfight|| February 8, 2015 ||{{flagicon|USA}} [[Los Angeles]], [[California|CA]]\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|POL}} [[Marcin Held]]  || Submission (heel hook) || Polaris 1||Superfight|| January 10, 2015 ||{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Cardiff]]\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|USA}} Zak Maxwell  || Submission (heel hook) || Metamoris 5||Superfight|| November 22, 2014 ||{{flagicon|USA}} [[Los Angeles]], [[California|CA]]\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win||{{flagicon|AUS}} Kit Dale  || 